about.summary: Convert data to 'GeoJSON' or 'TopoJSON' from various R classes, including vectors, lists, data frames, shape files, and spatial classes. 'geojsonio' does not aim to replace packages like 'sp', 'rgdal', 'rgeos', but rather aims to be a high level client to simplify conversions of data from and to 'GeoJSON' and 'TopoJSON'.

name: r-geojsonio
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "0.9.2" %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-geojsonio
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/geojsonio_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/geojsonio/geojsonio_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: c6a13cddf18463157eed9014772e69234af8f548a29f58a479c0f00df22e61d4

build:
  merge_build_host: true  # [win]
  number: 1
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
    - r-v8
    - r-crul
    - r-geojson >=0.2.0
    - r-jqr
    - r-jsonlite >=0.9.21
    - r-magrittr
    - r-maptools
    - r-readr >=0.2.2
    - r-rgeos
    - r-sf >=0.6
    - r-sp
  run:
    - r-base
    - r-v8
    - r-crul
    - r-geojson >=0.2.0
    - r-jqr
    - r-jsonlite >=0.9.21
    - r-magrittr
    - r-maptools
    - r-readr >=0.2.2
    - r-rgeos
    - r-sf >=0.6
    - r-sp

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('geojsonio')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('geojsonio')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: https://github.com/ropensci/geojsonio (devel), https://docs.ropensci.org/geojsonio (docs)
  license: MIT
  summary: Convert data to 'GeoJSON' or 'TopoJSON' from various R classes, including vectors, lists, data frames, shape files, and spatial classes. 'geojsonio' does
    not aim to replace packages like 'sp', 'rgdal', 'rgeos', but rather aims to be a high level client to simplify conversions of data from and to 'GeoJSON' and 'TopoJSON'.
  license_family: MIT
  license_file:
    - {{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/MIT
    - LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
    - xhochy
